<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Every generation that comes believes it can succeed in where the previous generation failed in finding happiness without God.</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">You will never be able to catch up to the happiness. Generations will come and go while your happiness and endeavors are nothing but temporary and meaningless.</p>
<p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">Nothing that we work for and obtain in this world will transfer with us to to the next. It all will be left behind.</p></body></html>